<div class="container breadcrumbs--hierarchy">
  <div class="col-sm-12">  首頁     > 台中市 > 澄清醫院</div>
</div>
<main>
  <div class="container">
    <section class="col-md-6 col-sm-12 box division">
      <div class="title">
        依科別尋找
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <% @categories.each do |category|%>
            <div class="col-md-2 col-xs-6">
              <%= category.name %>
            </div>
        <% end %>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="col-sm-12 box">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="information">
          <div class="information-header">
            <div class="thumbnail">
              照片
            </div>
            <div class="information-title">
              澄清醫院
              <span>推薦數/評論數/評分</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="information-body row">
            <div class="col-md-4 image">
              <%= image_tag("mapSample") %>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-8 about">
              關於本院:<br/>現演一底的天做？期學這定、片金兒希，心的員起。記老所是中舞教友幾，天無局吃林，自友著有、十上建大境辦立源公紅應香來，著的燈：外別金個開長統。人戰傷你線了今護條親買故總子：專開們道甚的去引生、為著雙歌美提時全你節費友面價。重前夜少雖較北眾，家經服但這題一大；具拉似；長合是！好發一他打年是黃臺過重多的分二我工國，發香臺取年作支道，紀界出可大灣望動散一會的性日。了起勢達謝品司，候一人我奇方美始國座位回現。思樣以一於反有密中慢讀說高往指術多！深因快力色出中些？國的些吃他強的看……車高戲要身的來備中：時試些區華。
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="col-md-6 box doctor">
      <div class="title">
        院科別排行
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-6">
          <div class="title sub-title">
            推薦科別
          </div>
          <div class="row">
            <% @goodCategories.each_with_index do |category, index|%>
                <div class="col-xs-12 rank">
                  <%= index + 1 %><%= category.name %>
                </div>
            <% end %>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">
          <div class="title sub-title">
            熱門科別
          </div>
          <div class="row">
            <% @goodCategories.each_with_index do |category, index|%>
                <div class="col-xs-12 rank">
                  <%= index + 1 %><%= category.name %>
                </div>
            <% end %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="col-md-6 box doctor">
      <div class="title">
        院醫生排行
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-6">
          <div class="title sub-title">
            推薦醫生
          </div>
          <div class="row">
            <% @goodDoctors.each_with_index do |doctor, index|%>
                <div class="col-xs-12 rank">
                  <%= index + 1 %><%= doctor.name %>
                </div>
            <% end %>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">
          <div class="title sub-title">
            推薦醫生
          </div>
          <div class="row">
            <% @goodDoctors.each_with_index do |doctor, index|%>
                <div class="col-xs-12 rank">
                  <%= index + 1 %><%= doctor.name %>
                </div>
            <% end %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="col-md-12 box comment">
      <div class="title">
        醫院最新科別評論
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <% @comments.each do |comment| %>
            <% unless comment.div_comment.nil? || comment.div_comment.empty? %>
                <div class="col-xs-4">
                  <div class="comment-box">
                    <p>評論者: user</p>
                    <p>對象： doctor</p>
                    <p>科別滿意度： 2.0</p>
                    <p>醫師滿意度： 4.0</p>
                    <p>科別評論：
                      <%= comment.div_comment %>
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>
            <% end %>
        <% end %>
      </div>
      <%= will_paginate @comments %>
    </section>
    <section class="col-md-12 box comment">
      <div class="title">
        醫院最新醫師評論
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <% @comments.each do |comment| %>
            <% unless comment.div_comment.nil? || comment.div_comment.empty? %>
                <div class="col-xs-4">
                  <div class="comment-box">
                    <p>評論者: user</p>
                    <p>對象： doctor</p>
                    <p>科別滿意度： 2.0</p>
                    <p>醫師滿意度： 4.0</p>
                    <p>科別評論：
                      <%= comment.div_comment %>
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>
            <% end %>
        <% end %>
      </div>
      <%= will_paginate @comments %>
    </section>
  </div>

</main>
